   Amplify your current data sets with net-new devices for extended reach
   Icon

Personalization

   Customize your messages across paid, earned, and programmatic efforts

As your partner, we make The Tapad Graph work for you

   Tapad works with brands, agencies and platforms to ingest device
   identifiers from their platforms or data stacks, expanding their graph
   with new devices at a household or individual level.

